Package org.anyframe.query

Provides interface for executing SQL queries or updates, initiating iteration over ResultSets And also provides exception class that is thrown when there is any problem executing the query

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DynamicSqlParameterSource This is a class for setting input argument which needed for executing the query statement
MappingInfo This is a class for the role of saving the mapping info of the defined table inside the table mappings.
QueryInfo This is a class for the role of saving the info about query statement defined in the query mappings.
QueryService This Service simplifies the use of JDBC and helps to avoid common errors.
ResultSetMapper This is a class for the role of mapping resultset to DTOs.
RowMetadataCallbackHandler This is a class for handling the task of setting the metadata from the ResultSet obtained after executing the query statement
SqlLoader This is a class for the role of loading the mapping infomration.
